One Move Captures White (3)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b Black to Play.\b0
\par White plays dansu with \'a1\'e2 and tries to live.
\par Frankly, ithis is a very careless move.
\par
\par This problem is very easy, but in a real game, there is a chance you might play without thinking and make a mistake. White's eyespace is narrow so please capture cleanly.
\par
\par }
