[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If black connects at 1, it ruins a good opportunity. You don't think it's the correct answer, do you?
\par
\par White plays 2 in seonsu, and then plays 4 and living effortlessly. It is a straight four shape.
\par }
