Diagram 2 (A Clever Move)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}{\f1\fmodern\fprq2\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It is a clever move for black to hane at 1, disregarding white's dansu.
\par
\par \pard\nowidctlpar\qj If white captures black at \b\f1 A\b0\f0 , black takes-back immediately at \'a1\'e3. White is short of eyespace and cannot live.
\par }
