Diagram 4 (Vital Point)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}{\f1\fmodern\fprq2\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \pard\nowidctlpar\qj Intially, it was mentioned that white's dansu at \b\f1 A\b0\f0  was a mistake.
\par \pard
\par White 1 in this diagram is the only way for white to live. As soon as a black took this vital point, there was no way for white to live.
\par
\par }
